{"tid":1345242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請正名「元朗恐襲」，並廣發出去","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:56:01.000Z","uid":64191,"like":186,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"326159e275229275b7a57c99e239ef05a0a2c368","tid":1345242,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:40:10.000Z","msg":"香港官方稱其為「糾紛」<br />\n睇過片段既人，一定認為係「暴動」、「暴亂」<br />\n然而，由於元朗事件係有組織、有計劃，且有龐大勢力撐腰，持續時間更為數小時以上，地點更係發生於公共場所、大眾群集之地<br />\n<br />\n受害民眾不是被故意針對，而係被無差別攻擊<br />\n有念及此，文宣及市民下一步宣傳，應該係以「元朗恐襲」為題，廣發出去<br />\n<br />\n但亦不要因此被轉移視線，應連同政府問題一併處理，視為政府開設既新戰線。"},{"pid":"b2f08d4274784561630f4db80ebaeddeab320809","tid":1345242,"uid":269643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"state terrorism"},{"pid":"1993c50ea43f2cc9b2e8b0894c31fdc9c3b12c58","tid":1345242,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4417f7252f3453887f0c5247a3593702ddc6987a","tid":1345242,"uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"Yuen Long Terrorist Attack<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f2f2e71ff8192f7aa8243604e4c36ed81a100a","tid":1345242,"uid":130162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3m89Zv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3m89Zv.png&h=a460777d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFCXiSR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFCXiSR.png&h=83236c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnCHuZw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnCHuZw.png&h=e40f8b62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhhDNMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhhDNMc.png&h=00cc28e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img sr